Title: [ANN] NAVIADDRESS - BLOCKCHAIN INFRASTRUCTURE ID PROJEKT! ICO Complete :)
Body: Naviaddress takes part in the CV Competition for Real Estate  The Crypto Valley Competition is a startup contest for blockchain projects. Each competition targets a specific industry, the current project is devoted to the Real Estate industry.  Lack of addressing has historically been a pain point for real estate, e-commerce and express delivery markets. Naviaddress provides an addressing layer over any digital map and can provide real estate developers with a naviaddress for their buildings on a very early stage of construction process even before getting a postal address, which could improve the experience of construction as well as advertising.  The CV competition is a great opportunity for us to grow awareness of the project and get an opportunity to scale our solution to other countries. We have already submitted our case and are looking forward to the results of the contest, which will be announced on the 27th of March at the CV Summit in Crypto Valley in Zug, Switzerland.  Let's keep our fingers crossed!

Title: [ANN] NAVIADDRESS - BLOCKCHAIN INFRASTRUCTURE ID PROJEKT! ICO Complete :)
Body: Progress Update #3 ‚Äì June 16th   Dear Community,   We have achieved some incredible results over the past few weeks! And even more is yet to come! Here is a brief summary of the things we have accomplished and a small sneak preview of our plans for the nearest future. Check it out!   ‚óè We have finalized and approved our Strategic Development roadmap for 2018 ‚Äì 2020. Our strategy is built on the Lean Startup methodology to ensure the build-measure-learn-feedback loop. This guarantees stable growth of our platform. We‚Äôve already started the implementation of the strategy by detailed analysis of the industries that cope with "pain of last-mile delivery".   ‚óè Customer development has gained traction. Our study of common pains in express delivery industry has signaled painpoints in: inefficient address verification processes, low couriers‚Äô productivity, undelivered post due to inaccurate addresses, etc. We are going to start several pilot projects with national delivery operators and e-commerce platforms in Russia within the coming weeks. This is to capture more insights and feedbacks from e-commerce and express delivery businesses and their customers to code and build into NAVI platform features and addressing services.[/b]   ‚óè Platform development is moving forward. Our Testnet Beta 0.2 is now live and we have been receiving productive feedback! You can now buy and sell Premium Naviaddresses and obtain them through auction; main smart contracts are upgradeable. Learn about our new Beta: https://t.me/naviaddressnews/93   ‚óè New Team member is onboard. New Team member is onboard. Andrey Gershun has joined the Naviaddress project in the role of Vice-President for Partnerships and Customer Development. Andrey has got his education from Moscow State University (Computer Science) and Harvard Business School. He worked for Ernst and Young, Platinum Software, and was the founder and COO for MAG Consulting. His 25-years of entrepreneurial and IT consulting experience will influence and enhance the future development of the Naviaddress platform significantly. Andrey is an IT-enthusiast, ERP, EAM and BI-systems experience professional, EMBA lecturer, founder of a popular open source project AlaSQL: http://alasql.org (github.com/agershun/alasql).   ‚óè Dmitri Moiseev, Naviaddress Co-Founder and CEO, spoke with TechBullion about the first fully functional blockchain addressing platform for any place and object. Learn how the project will develop in the next 3 years: https://www.techbullion.com/fully-functional-address-for-any-place-or-object-interview-with-dmitry-moiseev-ceo-co-founder-of-naviaddress/   ‚óè We are working on getting listed on a new exchange. We expect to receive a positive update by the end of this month!    Stay tuned and thank you for supporting our Team and the project!   Here are useful links: ‚Ä¢ https://github.com/naviworld/navi-token/; ‚Ä¢ Website: naviaddress.io ‚Ä¢ twitter.com/naviaddress ‚Ä¢ medium.com/naviaddress ‚Ä¢ https://t.me/naviaddressnews   Join our discussion on Reddit! https://reddit.com/r/Naviaddress   üîπNEWS May 10th | Progress Update #1: https://t.me/naviaddressnews/77 May 17th | Progress Update #2: https://t.me/naviaddressnews/82   NAVIADDRESS Community Naviaddress is a blockchain ID management platform which develops, markets and operates an address platform. The current platform is being deployed onto the blockchain. It will provide people and businesses with freedom and ability to create, obtain, own, lend and sell their digital addresses - naviaddresses - unified digital IDs for any place and object.

Body: Progress Update #4 ‚Äì July 4th  Dear Community,   The past few weeks we have been working on some exciting new opportunities that have a potential to boost our growth. We think that it is high time it share them with Naviaddress supporters! Learn about our accomplishments and of plans for the nearest future!  ‚óè Naviaddress joins the Enterprise Ethereum Alliance, the world's largest open source blockchain initiative. As a member of the EEA, Naviaddress will collaborate with industry leaders in pursuit of Ethereum-based enterprise technology best practices, open standards, and open-source reference architectures. Naviaddress aims to build the leading ID management platform to operate the storage and usage of unified digital IDs and establish the standard of human-machine interaction. Implementing user-friendly digital location identity contributes to the mass adoption of blockchain-based products and services for the benefits of common people in a daily life. Learn more: https://t.me/naviaddressnews/99  ‚óè Naviaddress team has completed the second stage of the pilot integration with DPD, one of the largest parcel delivery companies in Europe and a strategic partner of Alibaba in Russia, to identify exact pain point areas at address processing and parcel delivery stages where Naviaddress IDs can be implemented for the benefit of DPD customers, clients and employees. We also currently negotiate and plan to launch several pilot projects with express delivery and e-commerce operators to determine exact pain points related to their daily business and provide quantitative and qualitative evidence about how the Naviaddress solution can help improve internal efficiency in the delivery industry. Learn more about DPD pilot update: https://medium.com/@naviaddress/dpd-pilot-integration-update-fae4dccdba75.  ‚óè Naviaddress Referral Campaign is completed!  We want to thank all referral campaign participants for your interest and support of our initiative! During the campaign we were joined by 260.000 new Naviaddress supporters, and 121.000 of them have followed our campaign guidelines and received their rewards! This initiative has helped to build awareness about Naviaddress, and we hope that with more NAVI token holders we will soon see a boost in trade volume!  ‚óè Team Update: our project is getting stronger by recruiting the leading experts in their respective areas! Last week Ivan Borisov joined the Team as Naviaddress Solidity Engineer. Ivan spent more than 8 years in consulting industry and then moved to IT in 2016. He has proficient understanding and experience with writing Ethereum smart contracts.  ‚óè Upcoming Events in July: Meet Naviaddress team at blockchain Summit in Korea (July 12th - 13th) and World Blockchain Summit in Singapore (July, 19th).   Thank you for trusting our Team and supporting our project!

Body: KuCoin Community Coin Vote  The People‚Äôs Exchange is again giving a voice to the community in order to choose the winner of a free listing. This time it will be a Telegram vote. Participating in the Community Coin Vote is a great way to reach a larger audience and thus increase the awareness about Naviaddress. Therefore, we believe listing on their exchange would increase accessibility to our tokens and increase the adoption and utility of our addressing solution!  HOW TO VOTE? You can vote today, July 12th 18:00 UTC+8 and voting will remain open until July 15th 18:00 UTC+8.  ‚Ä¢ Make sure you sign-up on KuCoin. If you do so, you will be disqualified. ‚Ä¢ Don‚Äôt spam, remain polite and listen to the admins. Offenders will be banned and votes revoked.  Thank you for supporting Naviaddress! Body: Naviaddress for an Event: Bringing People Together in the Digital Age  Setting up special events, conferences, workshops and meet-ups is key to growing your business. But explaining the way, how to get to an event location can take quite an amount of time especially for remote locations or multi building complexes or art spaces.  Nowadays simple postal address is not enough. Naviaddress helps to solve the problem quickly and permanently. It works as a  ‚Äúsmart address‚Äù, where users can assign and store relevant information in the digital ID. All you need is to add details to naviaddress card, such as address, detailed route description, time of the event, necessary details about dress-code and links for social media channels.  That is easy to have the information about your event in a one card, which you can share with one click.  Event businesses  are among the early adopters who are using Naviaddress to improve customer satisfaction.  The organizers of the last week charity event HEART TO HEART in Limassol created  6-digit naviaddress - https://naviaddress.com/357/%23010 - to share the information with the customers in one click.  Start using Naviaddress while planning special occasions! Download Naviaddress App now and create your naviaddress for any upcoming events!

Author: NAVIADDRESS
Title: [ANN] NAVIADDRESS - BLOCKCHAIN INFRASTRUCTURE ID PROJEKT! ICO Complete :)
Body: Frequently Asked Questions: NAVI after ICO  Dear community,  After completing our ICO on March 31, we have been getting a lot of questions from you regarding different aspects of our future. We have selected those questions that we receive most frequently and we would like to share the answers with you!  How many Navi Tokens are we supposed to get per eth?  We will determine timestamps for each transaction during ICO. Then we will retrieve the average rates for BTC/US$ and ETH/US$ for those particular timestamps. These rates will be used to calculate amount of NAVI allocated to every contributor.  When NAVI will be listed on an exchange?  We are negotiating with several exchanges at the moment and will release exchange info in the upcoming days.  Does the company plan to buy own tokens?  No.  Is there any lock up persiod?  Tokens for Pre-Sale and the great majority of ICO participants are not locked up. The Pool of total unsold 500M NAVIs (the team, the company and the platform development reserves) is subject to the following lock-up restrictions during 36 months after the end of our ICO.  6 months complete lock-up: NAVIs are gradually released for sale only upon expiration of 6 months following the end date of ICO; 30 months lock-up graduate release: NAVIs are released for sale in 30 installments of 1/30th of the Pool on the 30th day following the last date of 6 months lock-up period and each of the releases thereafter.  What are token metrics to add to MEW?  If you need to add on MEW or Metamask, here are the details:  Symbol : NAVI  Decimals 18  Address:  0x588047365df5ba589f923604aac23d673555c623  What wallet can I use?  All wallets compatible with / supporting ERC20.  How to set up an ERC20-compatible Ethereum wallet?  We recommend to use MEW.  How to send tokens from my ether wallet?  That can be done using ERC20 token sending mechanism from your wallet.  How to sell tokens?  Tokens will be sent via exchange. We will will release the. We will keep you updated regarding the exchange info.  How to buy tokens?  Tokens will be bought via exchange. We will will release the. We will keep you updated regarding the exchange info.  What will be the price of token at the exchange?  NAVI price shall be determined by the market forces of supply and demand at exchanges. We will release the exchange info in the upcoming days.    As always, we would like to warn you that there are still scammers trying to swindle your money. Make sure to receive all information regarding NAVI in our official channels!  Website: https://naviaddress.io https://twitter.com/naviaddress https://facebook.com/naviaddressplatform https://t.me/naviaddress  We want to thank all of our supporters for trusting Naviaddress project and our Team!

Author: NAVIADDRESS
Title: [ANN] NAVIADDRESS - BLOCKCHAIN INFRASTRUCTURE ID PROJEKT! ICO Complete :)
Body: We are changing the way people get to places and change an address of their physical location. We used to first build and/or move in our home and then get the address. Naviaddress provides a user with the ability to choose the digital address ID first and then assign it to his/her living location. You can move to another house but your naviaddress stays the same. Here is the example - our Moscow developers' office moved 3 times for last two years but our Naviaddress 7495 0022 - remained the same. You can assign any information to your digital address and that is great for people who have no  permanent residence but want to have an opportunity to be reached. Also it would simplify the way of transportation and/or delivery things (the "last mile" issue, for example). Just imagine that you would not have to explain a complicated route to somebody anymore, but instead give them a 9-digits code.

Title: [ANN] NAVIADDRESS - BLOCKCHAIN INFRASTRUCTURE ID PROJEKT! ICO Complete :)

Author: NAVIADDRESS
Title: [ANN] NAVIADDRESS - BLOCKCHAIN INFRASTRUCTURE ID PROJEKT! ICO Complete :)
Body: Naviaddress announces strategic partnership with Accum Trillion Capital (Blockchain Industrial Investment Fund)    Naviaddress, a blockchain ID management project, which provides users with naviaddresses as unified digital IDs for any places or objects in physical and virtual worlds, announced strategic partnership with ACCUM TRILLION CAPITAL, a management and consulting company for Blockchain Industrial Investment Fund. The company has significant influence and local resources in China. It is involved in blockchain technology related investments and provides one-stop solution to blockchain projects. Accum Trillion has been investor in projects QTUM, VEN, GXS, OMG, PAY and several other projects. Naviaddress team is confident that ACCUM TRILLION CAPITAL will facilitate expansion of Naviaddress platform and services into Chinese market and assist in identifying local partners.  Dmitry Moiseev, Co-founder and CEO of Naviaddress, made a statement: ‚ÄúWe are expanding our community and network of partners to Asia. It is highly important for faster development and global adoption of our address platform. We are confident that Accum Trillion Capital will assist Naviaddress to identify business potential and long-term partners in China for further localization and adoption of the platform in mainland China‚Äù.  As of February 2018, there are 1.5 million naviaddresses in Naviaddress addressing system, including 1.3 million business naviaddresses, with the total number of registered active Naviaddress app users exceeding 60,000 people (including web, iOS and Android). Beta version of the platform on the blockchain was released for public testing on March 2, 2018. Naviaddress is building partnerships with large address holders in delivery, e-retail and HoReCa businesses, such as Booking.com, DPD, and plan cooperation and integration with State Postal Services, AliExpress, Amazon, NinjaVan, etc. to share verified addresses with the platform.   With over 55% of NaviTokens sold so far, and aim to raise $20 million in total during ICO, there is enough traction to partner with some major players in China in delivery and e-retail, hospitality, transportation and urban planning. Once the addressing system is deployed on the blockchain, Naviaddress will enable 4 billion people in the world living without addresses to obtain and share digital postal delivery naviaddresses, verified by a transaction on the blockchain at almost no cost. Usage of naviaddresses will enable local governments to provide more citizens with essential services and create new markets for e-retailers and delivery businesses.

Title: [ANN] NAVIADDRESS - BLOCKCHAIN INFRASTRUCTURE ID PROJEKT! ICO Complete :)
Body: Naviaddress ICO Review  NAVIADDRESS - a unified digital ID for any place and object in real and virtual worlds.  Naviaddress aims to create a decentralised global unified address platform for real and virtual worlds. Using a patented technology Naviaddress developed a platform with a capability to assign a digital address to any location with geocoordinate precision: Same in any language, cross-cultural: digits only Addressing any object or place: hybrid postal address and geotag More than just an address: additional information (contacts, ‚Äúlast mile‚Äù, etc.), users‚Äô content  Naviaddress solves wide range of mapping problems. It provides a representation of location or well-defined space with significant value for social or economical activity. It‚Äôs also important for  statistics collecting and identification of postal endpoints.  More details about this token & project please find in review of our analytics team on this link

Author: NAVIADDRESS
Title: [ANN] NAVIADDRESS - BLOCKCHAIN INFRASTRUCTURE ID PROJEKT! ICO Complete :)
Body: Everything you wanted to know about NaviTokens   Over the last few months we have been getting a lot of questions regarding NVTs, their supply, usage and other details. That is why we would like to share key information about NaviTokens with our community.   Basic information   NVT is a smart token, exchange medium and an incentive. NVT is based on the ERC20 standard.   Total supply: 1,000,000,000 Allocated for ICO: 400,000,000   Already sold at pre-ICO: 200,000,000 Left for ICO sale starting March 01, 2018: 200,000,000   ICO Information  Price: 0.05 USD We deliberately offer single minimum price for all participants at pre-ICO and ICO stages to avoid any price dump in the short term. We have not provided, and do not offer bonuses and bounty points, credits and whatsoever. We also do not trade discounts. All these practices ruin the token price at the exchange after the placement and do not address token holders midterm economic goals.   We accept Ethers, Bitcoins and Fiat currencies. The conversion of ETH/BTC to US$ to NVT will be done after the ICO closing using the data from https://www.cryptocompare.com/api/.   We will determine timestamps for each transaction (BlockTrail for BTC and Etherscan for ETH) during ICO. Then we will retrieve the average rates for BTC/US$ and ETH/US$ for those particular timestamps. These rates will be used to calculate amount of NVT allocated to every contributor.   NaviTokens will be distributed within 7 days after the ICO ends.   How does the Naviaddress token (NVT) function within the platform and why is it needed?   NaviToken is a utility token. Naviaddresses are exchanged for NaviTokens. Premium naviaddresses (1-5 digits) will be purchased by users. Custom naviaddresses (6-8 digits and more) will be paid by the platform. We are building freemium model.   We also plan to use tokens reserved for development of the platform and ecosystem around it in three major ways: 1) Incentivize local national partners to work with the platform by co-investing with them into JV - we will invest our tokens (5-10%< of overall development fund of the JV). Sell country/regional containers of premium naviaddresses (1 to 5 digits) for NaviTokens through auction to local partners (could be JV) with proven competence in the subscription business so that they will lease naviaddresses to local businesses for fiat and make money. The result of this transaction - all nominal price in tokens for sold naviaddresses will be burnt by the platform while the premium - a difference between market price and nominal price - will be retained by the platform as the revenue. Our current forecast shows that 150 million NavTokens will be burnt if the Platform sells 30 national containers of premium naviaddresses.   2) Incentivize big verified address holders (DHL, DPD, others) to share verified addresses with the platform. We will need NVTs to incentivize them to share.   3) Incentivize GIS experts to verify currently unverified addresses. As you see, we need to have a quite sizable ecosystem development fund. We intend to play long term.   We have published the smart-contract in our profile on GitHub. Check details: https://github.com/naviworld/navi-token/.   You can sign up on our website ‚Äì www.naviaddress.io.  The ‚ÄòRegister for ICO‚Äô button adds you to the registration procedure to join the whitelist. Please fill in the application online.   Contact us!   We are encouraging the community to ask questions in our Telegram Community that way everyone can join the discussion and learn from other people‚Äôs experiences / enquiries. https://t.me/naviaddress/   You can also reach us through any of these channels:   Twitter Facebook Medium Reddit

Author: NAVIADDRESS
Title: [ANN] NAVIADDRESS - BLOCKCHAIN INFRASTRUCTURE ID PROJEKT! ICO Complete :)
Body: Dear Navi supporters,  We have received many questions on how NVTs shall be distributed among purchasers at our ICO stage that starts on March 1, 2018.  To address all that questions, we have developed and publish here a procedure on NVTs sale at ICO stage.  Procedure On the last day of the pre-ICO we will calculate and publish the amount of NVTs available for the ICO stage. We will also group the members of WL into 2 categories: "early birds" and the rest - based on the dates they've applied for registration. "Early birds" stands for all registered before February 25th 3pm CET.  Further placement of NVTs will go in 3 phases:   ‚Ä¢ Phase I starts on March 01st 3pm CET and goes for 24 hours - until March 2nd 3pm CET. Only "early bird" members are eligible for the Phase I. We will determine the pro-rata cap for this phase as the total amount of NVTs available for the ICO divided by the number of "early birds" members in the WL. Participants will be offered to acquire number of tokens limited by such cap. Thus "early birds" members are guaranteed to participate in token generation event unless all NVTs would be sold before the ICO start.   ‚Ä¢ Phase II starts on March 03rd 3pm CET and goes for 24 hours - until March 4th 3pm CET. All "white-listed" members are eligible for the Phase II. We will determine the pro-rata cap for this phase as the total amount of NVTs remained after the Phase I (out of total amount of NVT available for the ICO) divided by the number of all "white-listed" members. Participants will be offered to acquire number of tokens limited by such cap.   ‚Ä¢ Phase III - a "gas war" - starts on March 5th 3pm CET and goes till the end of ICO on March 31st 3pm CET. For this phase number of tokens left after Phase I & II will be offered to all members of WL. FIFO rule applied. No upper limits on the amount of NVT to acquire. The more gas provided to register transaction - the better chances to get as much as you want before others come.  Example: Let's assume that only 200M NVTs are available for the ICO as of March 1 3pm CET. Also assume that total WL is 10K people with 5K are "early birds". Phase I: Cap is set at 40K NVTs per person (200M NVTs / 5K "early birds"). "Early birds" are offered to acquire as much as 40K NVTs @ US$0.05 or up to US$ 2000. Let's assume that 160M NVTs are acquired in this Phase. Phase II: Cap is set at 4K NVTs per person (40M NVTs / 10K "white-listed"). "White-listed" are offered to acquire as much as 4K NVTs @ US$0.05 or up to US$ 200. Let's assume that 30M NVTs are acquired at this Phase II.  Phase III: 10M NVTs are still unsold. All "white-listed" members are free to acquire any amount of NVTs out of available pool by sending their contributions. Author: NAVIADDRESS
Title: [ANN] NAVIADDRESS - BLOCKCHAIN INFRASTRUCTURE ID PROJEKT! ICO Complete :)
Body: Thanks for your question. Naviaddress is a completely new take on the current navigation and addressing systems. Three large cases for why it's needed: 1. Lack of addresses as a part of ID for 4 billion people in the world. Once the addressing system is deployed on the blockchain, Naviaddress will enable 4 billion people in the world living without addresses to obtain digital postal delivery naviaddresses, verified by a transaction on the blockchain at almost no cost. Usage of naviaddresses will enable local governments to provide more citizens with essential services and create new markets for e-retailers and delivery businesses (AliBaba, Amazon, etc.). 2.  With online and shared economy getting globalised conventional language specific addressing systems becomes a hurdle for quick, transparent and cost-efficient transactions between buyers and sellers. Today, up to 20% and up to 80% of addresses in developed and developing countries respectively are not verified from the first time due to mistakes in address spelling, address verification and ‚Äúlast mile‚Äù navigation problems. Issues with address verification create billions of US dollar wastes in e-retail and delivery industries.  Naviaddress will provide trustless verified by transaction and geo coordinates precise ID of users‚Äô locations for online and delivery businesses. Our solution will cut the waste drastically. 3. International tourists and expats remained inaccessible for local hotels, cafes and restaurants. This result in lost sales. Naviaddress will provide authentication and easy last mile navigation for local HoReCa and retail outlets due to only digits, no language-specific, digital address, which is easy to find, share and communicate.    Deployment of Naviaddress system on the blockchain will provide for the following: 1. People and businesses get the freedom and ability to create, obtain, own, lend and sell their digital addresses. We call them naviaddresses - unified digital IDs for any place or object in real and virtual worlds- and they have all features to become new global addressing standard. No more shall we be dependent on state and municipal agencies -blockchain technology has enabled us to provide you with a naviaddress, trustless and verified by a transaction. 2. Naviaddresses and rights to them will be stored in a decentralized way, detached from Naviaddress company and practically forever. 3. Naviaddress ownership registration in favour of a user with smart contracts application. 4. Issue and circulation of NaviToken that will be used as the only currency to buy/sell/lend naviaddresses as well as the incentive for building the ecosystem and provide services within it.  You can find a lot more details on our ICO website https://naviaddress.io We're currently updating it with more information. You can also reach us for real time conversations at https://t.me/naviaddress

Title: [ANN] NAVIADDRESS - BLOCKCHAIN INFRASTRUCTURE ID PROJEKT! ICO Complete :)
Body: Thanks for your question. Actually language is also an issue and remembering an address, so pointing it on a map doesn't really solve it...  Here are 3 large cases for why it's needed:  1. Lack of addresses as a part of ID for 4 billion people in the world. Once the addressing system is deployed on the blockchain, Naviaddress will enable 4 billion people in the world living without addresses to obtain digital postal delivery naviaddresses, verified by a transaction on the blockchain at almost no cost. Usage of naviaddresses will enable local governments to provide more citizens with essential services and create new markets for e-retailers and delivery businesses (AliBaba, Amazon, etc.).  2.  With online and shared economy getting globalised conventional language specific addressing systems becomes a hurdle for quick, transparent and cost-efficient transactions between buyers and sellers. Today, up to 20% and up to 80% of addresses in developed and developing countries respectively are not verified from the first time due to mistakes in address spelling, address verification and ‚Äúlast mile‚Äù navigation problems. Issues with address verification create billions of US dollar wastes in e-retail and delivery industries.  Naviaddress will provide trustless verified by transaction and geo coordinates precise ID of users‚Äô locations for online and delivery businesses. Our solution will cut the waste drastically.  3. International tourists and expats remained inaccessible for local hotels, cafes and restaurants. This result in lost sales. Author: NAVIADDRESS
Title: [ANN] NAVIADDRESS - BLOCKCHAIN INFRASTRUCTURE ID PROJEKT! ICO Complete :)
Body: Dear Navi supporters, We have received many questions on how NVTs shall be distributed among purchasers at our ICO stage that starts on March 1, 2018.  To address all that questions, we have developed and publish here a procedure on NVTs sale at ICO stage.  Procedure: On the last day of the pre-ICO we will calculate and publish the amount of NVTs available for the ICO stage. We will also group the members of WL into 2 categories: "early birds" and the rest - based on the dates they've applied for registration. "Early birds" stands for all registered before February 25th 3pm CET.  Further placement of NVTs will go in 3 phases:   o Phase I starts on March 01st 3pm CET and goes for 24 hours - until March 2nd 3pm CET. Only "early bird" members are eligible for the Phase I. We will determine the pro-rata cap for this phase as the total amount of NVTs available for the ICO divided by the number of "early birds" members in the WL. Participants will be offered to acquire number of tokens limited by such cap. Thus "early birds" members are guaranteed to participate in token generation event unless all NVTs would be sold before the ICO start.   o Phase II starts on March 03rd 3pm CET and goes for 24 hours - until March 4th 3pm CET. All "white-listed" members are eligible for the Phase II. We will determine the pro-rata cap for this phase as the total amount of NVTs remained after the Phase I (out of total amount of NVT available for the ICO) divided by the number of all "white-listed" members. Participants will be offered to acquire number of tokens limited by such cap.   o Phase III - a "gas war" - starts on March 5th 3pm CET and goes till the end of ICO on March 31st 3pm CET. For this phase number of tokens left after Phase I & II will be offered to all members of WL. FIFO rule applied. No upper limits on the amount of NVT to acquire. The more gas provided to register transaction - the better chances to get as much as you want before others come.  Example: Let's assume that only 200M NVTs are available for the ICO as of March 1 3pm CET. Also assume that total WL is 10K people with 5K are "early birds". Phase I: Cap is set at 40K NVTs per person (200M NVTs / 5K "early birds"). "Early birds" are offered to acquire as much as 40K NVTs @ US$0.05 or up to US$ 2000. Let's assume that 160M NVTs are acquired in this Phase. Phase II: Cap is set at 4K NVTs per person (40M NVTs / 10K "white-listed"). "White-listed" are offered to acquire as much as 4K NVTs @ US$0.05 or up to US$ 200. Let's assume that 30M NVTs are acquired at this Phase II.  Phase III: 10M NVTs are still unsold. All "white-listed" members are free to acquire any amount of NVTs out of available pool by sending their contributions. We will monitor the subscription amounts based on the time stamps of transactions until all NVT got sold.  Thank you for your trust in Naviaddress project and our team!

Title: [ANN] NAVIADDRESS - BLOCKCHAIN INFRASTRUCTURE ID PROJEKT! ICO Complete :)
Body: Hi, thank you for your interest in our project!  As for us running out of tokens too soon - well, we encourage everyone who want to participate to go through KYC beforehand not to have to wait for registration during ICO.  As for the need of blockchain solution, there are several reasons.Once we migrate to Blockchain there will be obvious value in trustless and verified ID for users including business  users to transact over user naviaddress. Then, blockchain allows Naviaddress users to stay independent from us, as a central storage of their own meta-data. All the information, including contacts, pictures, last mile, website links, etc, that is attached to naviaddress by its owner, is beyond our control. So, the owner of a naviaddress is protected from any kind of hostile or sloppy actions from our side or any third parties.

Author: NAVIADDRESS
Title: [ANN] NAVIADDRESS - BLOCKCHAIN INFRASTRUCTURE ID PROJEKT! ICO Complete :)
Body: WEB - FACEBOOK - TWITTER - TELEGRAM - LINKEDIN - MEDIUM  Naviaddress is a blockchain infrastructure ID management software for any place and object NAVIADDRESS is a first global decentralized addressing system, which allows users to create random or unique digital address (Naviaddress) to any location as well as event worldwide.The patent pending technology encodes postal address and geotag into a digit address (called ‚Äúnaviaddress‚Äù) by creating a pin on the map and assigning a naviaddress. It allows to add comments or upload photos to make it easier to find, send naviaddress to friends, partners, taxi or delivery service. The platform allows to get free address to a location, objects, people via their smartphones in real and virtual reality.  Naviaddress platform serves as a solution to pain points in several areas: The last mile delivery problem: up to 20% of parcels are undelivered for the first time. Last mile delivery issues damage consumer experience. Leadership in the last mile delivery is the next step in creating competitive advantage in e-commerce market. The destination point/route communication as well as an authenticity of accommodation and services in HoReCa, Taxi and Transportation industries for international tourists and expats. The opportunity for common people to get and use a naviaddress which combines in one number an object (house, apartment, location, place of interest) or event, its postal/delivery address  and its geocoordinates.   The deployment of the addressing system onto the blockchain enables the Company to create and maintain a global decentralized database of verified and trusted postal/delivery and user generated addresses. With no dependency on single source and authority. The platform shall provide for regular acquisition, verification of addresses, turning them into naviaddresses with embedded metadata, provision of  naviaddresses to platform users. NaviaddressToken (NVT) will be used as proprietary value medium in  transactions with naviaddresses. It will provide for secure, fast and cost-effective transaction processing. NVT will serve as incentive for the platform promotion, adoption and further development.   OUR VISION  We proclaim that: Addresses must have a simple standard format throughout the world; Addresses can be created not only by governments but by any person or group; An address is much more than just a text line: it should also reflect a geo-position and a digital description of a location.  Our aim is to create a modern and easy-to-use international addressing system, which will give rise to a plethora of addresses: international addresses; unified addresses, easy to reference; flexible addresses; and, more importantly, addresses that are easy to obtain (accessible even to those individuals who would be living on an unnamed street or an unnumbered building).  THE NAVIADDRESS PLATFORM  The Naviaddress Platform is a decentralized software solution based on cutting edge blockchain technology. The main goal of the Naviaddress Platform is to create and develop a worldwide universal digital address solution. To allow this, Naviaddress is developing its own user incentive program based on NaviToken‚Ñ¢ tokens (NVT)(further discussed below). The Naviaddress Platform will promote the expansion of the System by issuing and sharing NVTs with Users who subscribe to any Naviaddress products, such as web and mobile applications, chat bots and so on. The Naviaddress Platform is gathering a community of geography experts and incentivizing creation and verification of world addresses. The main advantage of purchasing a NVT is the right to a naviaddress and the right to modify and update metadata related to such address. Information on such naviaddresses will be published and made available publicly on the Naviaddress System.  Main actors  Platform. The Naviaddress Platform is created and managed by the Naviaddress Platform Operator. Developer. Developers receive NVTs by creating new locations and extending the services and products. These activities are typically supported and rewarded by the Naviaddress Platform. Customer. Customers have the right to acquire rights to a naviaddress and publish this information within the System in the blockchain ledger. Every Platform member is eligible to exchange naviaddresses for NVTs. User. Individuals who use naviaddress applications and activities.   NaviTokenS‚Ñ¢  A NVT is a unit of defined value internal to the Platform that may be used by any of the actors outlined above in acquiring or exchanging rights to naviaddresses, services or any other thing within the Platform. NVTs could also be used to promote the System by awarding NVTs to Users for certain actions within the Naviaddress Platform: registration, invitation of others, creation of popular Custom naviaddresses and other activities. Ultimately, NVTs will be used to stimulate Platform promotion, adoption and development.      DEVELOPMENT ROADMAP  ‚óè     2015   Naviaddress incorporation, patent filing, MVP developed, Angel round US$500K raised; ‚óè     2016   The first application release, integration with UBER; ‚óè     2017 Q1         Seed round US$2MM received; ‚óè     2017 Q2         Strategic partnership with Booking.com; ‚óè     2017 Q3         Naviaddress app user base reaches 100 000 users; ‚óè     2017 Q3         Naviaddress blockchain protocol development initiated; ‚óè     2017 Q4        Token Generation Event/TGE & NVTs will become available on exchanges; ‚óè     2018 Q1         Naviaddress ledger, obtaining the right to naviaddresses smart-contracts; ‚óè     2018 Q2         Implementation of the blockchain protocol within the existing application; ‚óè     2018 Q2         Launch of the incentive program for a new free Naviaddress Platform; ‚óè     2018 Q3         Transfer smart contracts; ‚óè     2018 Q3-Q4   Business integration and partnership initiatives                              (DiDi, AirBnB, Alibaba, DHL, Amazon and many more);   OUR TEAM  More than just a great technological project, Naviaddress is also a team that works hard for the project.      SOCIAL  Learn more about the NAVIADDRESS initiative on our website or contact us via email, and join our social media channels:  Contact us at: feedback@naviworldcorp.com Or at:  ico-nvt@chaineum.com   WEB - FACEBOOK - TWITTER - TELEGRAM - LINKEDIN - MEDIUM
